Teri Copley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teri_Copley 0 Teri Copley (born May 10, 1961) is an American actress and model. She is known for role on the American NBC/syndicated television series We Got It Made which premiered in 1983, she co-starred on the 1985 CBS television series I Had Three Wives, and appeared in the 1990 pilot episode of Match Game 90. She appeared in the 1984 television film I Married a Centerfold and the 1992 film Brain Donors. She posed nude and was the cover girl for Playboy for the November 1990 issue. In the 1990s Copley became a born-again Christian and slowly eased her way out of celebrity Hollywood.She released a book, Conversations Between a Girl and Her God.
